%N A396532 First column of the triangular array with T(0, m) = binomial(2*m, m) and T(n, m) = T(n - 1, m + 3) - T(n - 1, m + 2).
%C A396532 The rows are generated by iterating the operator E^2*Delta, where E is the forward shift operator, E(f(m)) = f(m + 1), and Delta = E - 1 is the forward difference operator. Equivalently, E^2*Delta = E^2*(E - 1) = E^3 - E^2.
%F A396532 a(n) = Sum_{j=0..n} (-1)^(n - j)*binomial(n, j)*binomial(2*(2*n + j), 2*n + j).
%F A396532 a(n) = (1/Pi)*Integral_{x = 0..4} x^(2*n)*(x - 1)^n/sqrt(x*(4 - x)) dx.
